{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should not change the value of this property directly. This property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contains a non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" value while the annotation view is visible on the map. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view is queued, waiting to be reused, the value is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object currently associated with the view."}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/annotation"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/annotation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"annotation","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation"}],"fragments":[{"text":"annotation","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)annotation","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L126"}},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/annotation":{"abstract":[{"text":"The annotation object currently associated with the view.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"annotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/annotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/annotation"}}}